            . I am a pawnbroker. On the 28th<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183409040079"></xptr>of July, the prisoner came to my house, and bought a watch- he offered me two or three pieces of silver, which I took in part payment - this is the silver.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340904-151-person891">
