            . I am a pawnbroker. I produce five spoons, which the prisoner sold to me, on Monday, the 28th of July - I asked whose they were - he said they were his own.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was turned out of doors, through my mother-in-law, which is the reason of my distress.</p>
